data.description: Welcome home to the exclusive and prestigious village of Pinecrest. This gated home boasts over one acre of beautiful landscaping, including fruit trees, pool, and a quaint pond with a waterfall. The master bedroom suite has a sitting area overlooking the pool and an over sized walk in closet. The kitchen was renovated in 2017 with stainless steel appliances, granite counter tops, and room to seat more than 10 people!Never worry about hurricane season again this home has a 65 kilo watt underground generator. This home has a new roof that was installed in 2019! Appraisal performed 11/18/2016 at $1.785. full inspection report and copy of appraisal upon request.
